  "title": "Document Controller",
  "description": "<p>Our esteemed client in the <strong>Construction industry</strong> is seeking a <strong>Document Controller </strong>to join their dynamic team:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Employment Type: </strong>Permanent</li>\n  <li><strong>Position:</strong> Document Controller</li>\n  <li><strong>Location:</strong> Redhill</li>\n  <li><strong>Working Hours:</strong> Monday to Friday, Office Hours</li>\n  <li><strong>Salary Package:</strong> Up to $5,000 + Bonus</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Establish, maintain, and ensure the ongoing accuracy of the central document management repository for all project-related files.</li>\n  <li>Execute the filing, storage, and timely retrieval of documentation to support project efficiency.</li>\n  <li>Administer the formal process for issuing, tracking, and revising documents in strict compliance with internal protocols and project specifications.</li>\n  <li>Facilitate the controlled distribution of documentation to relevant internal and external project participants.</li>\n  <li>Maintain accurate and up-to-date logs for all document transmittals and submissions.</li>\n  <li>Provide dedicated support to project leadership and team members regarding document access, status, and compliance matters.</li>\n  <li>Uphold and enforce protocols for version control, confidentiality, and quality assurance of all documents.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>At least 2 years of experience as a Document Controller or in a similar role.</li>\n  <li>Solid knowledge of document control standards and best practices.</li>\n  <li>Proficient in with EDMS and Microsoft Office (Word, Excel, PowerPoint).</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Ready to apply? Here’s how:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Click the APPLY button, or</li>\n  <li>Email your resume (in MS Word or PDF format) to <a href=\"mailto:adelin@intuitrecruitment.com\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>adelin@intuitrecruitment.com</strong>.</a> Include the job title in your email subject line for prompt processing.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><em><strong>Only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</strong></em></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>By submitting your application, you consent to the collection and use of your personal data under Personal Data Protection Act (PDPA).</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Adelin Chong | EA Personnel Reg No.: R1875641</p>\n<p>Intuit Recruitment Pte Ltd | EA License No.: 25C2793</p>",
